These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, bus, jet-ski, trike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Transport   | bus | roller | car | snowmobile | trike | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: sports, epic, spy, comedy, mystery, romance
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | sports | spy | romance | mystery | epic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
6 different games are played: poker, domino, mah-jongg, chess, canasta, scrabble
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing poker##1
4. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
5. the person playing chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Game   | domino | mah-jongg | canasta | poker | scrabble | chess |

