2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |   3    |    4    |      5      |  6  |
| City   | liverpool | san-francisco | boston | prague | venice | nizza |

