2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |     4     |   5    |    6    |
| Sport   | water-polo | cycling | basketball | skateboarding | soccer | biathlon |

