3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |      3      |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Beverage   | milk | 7up | iced-tea | cola | sprite | fanta |

