4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing whist##1
6. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4      |      5      |   6   |
